---
import { Info, Train, Boat } from "../icons";
---

<section
  class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-gutter py-stack-xl"
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter">
    <div class="md:col-span-7 lg:col-span-8">
      <span class="text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-stack-sm block"
        >Overview</span
      >
      <h2 class="font-headline text-headline-h2 mb-stack-md">
        A Tale of Two Towns
      </h2>
      <div
        class="space-y-stack-md text-on-surface-variant font-body-lg leading-relaxed"
      >
        <p>
          Monterosso al Mare is the largest of the five coastal villages known
          as the Cinque Terre. The village is divided into two distinct parts:
          the old town and the new town, connected by a single tunnel that
          serves as a portal between centuries.
        </p>
        <p>
          In the new area, Fegina, visitors are greeted by vibrant umbrellas and
          the only extensive sand beach in the region. Cross through the tunnel,
          and you enter the historic heart—a labyrinth of narrow "carruggi"
          (alleys), medieval ruins, and pastel-hued dwellings that climb the
          steep terraced hillsides.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-5 lg:col-span-4">
      <div
        class="bg-surface-container p-stack-lg rounded-lg editorial-shadow border border-outline-variant/30 h-fit"
      >
        <h3
          class="font-headline-h3 text-headline-h3 mb-stack-lg flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <Info className="text-primary" />
          Quick Facts
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-stack-lg">
          <li class="border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-stack-sm">
            <span class="text-outline uppercase block">Population</span>
            <span class="font-body-md font-bold"
              >Approx. 1,400 permanent residents</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-stack-sm">
            <span class="text-outline uppercase block">Best Known For</span>
            <span class="font-body-md font-bold"
              >Sandy Beaches &amp; Ancient Lemon Trees</span
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="text-outline uppercase block">Connection</span>
            <div class="flex gap-stack-md mt-stack-xs">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1 font-body-md font-bold"
                ><Train className="text-secondary" dimension="18px" />
                Train</span
              >
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1 font-body-md font-bold"
                ><Boat className="text-secondary" dimension="18px" />
                Boat</span
              >
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section
  class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-gutter py-stack-xl"
>
  <div
    class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden editorial-shadow grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 items-center"
  >
    <div class="p-stack-xl">
      <span class="text-secondary uppercase tracking-wider mb-stack-sm block"
        >Gastronomy</span
      >
      <h2 class="font-headline text-headline-h2 mb-stack-md italic">
        Acciughe di Monterosso
      </h2>
      <p
        class="font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-stack-lg leading-relaxed"
      >
        Monterosso is world-renowned for its salted anchovies. Caught using
        traditional methods, these "Silver of the Sea" are celebrated every
        September during a dedicated festival. Pair them with a glass of local
        Cinque Terre DOC white wine for the ultimate coastal experience.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="h-px bg-outline-variant grow"></div>
        <span class="italic text-outline">A local legacy since 1900</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative h-full min-h-100">
      <img
        alt="Acciughe di Monterosso"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/ADBb0ugFxcUZqdVEOGqy6PDk7pfLADv1EanFqlPD2GiTUWR2Fi6cXL24fiu3r1wdTgpnYZoizLCCTXwlWEV0KcZytrxkRf1lGFjIp2C_ZqtTD7K0fkujR7axHVzathJ3IgHvRm_3Wq-KBatwytuDrUQSVeBVsGjVq2V2rJxJzWuFwVDM5BHl-JL-cJk2-0OmnDBps6SoSbJh1eWcvetKc6NaRM_4B0jYwL_ymRtp6pK55v4JIVLSBSTPlKshBOdO"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
